content:
Sure, I'd be happy to list out the art forms we discussed earlier in order of increasing cost:

1. Warli art
2. Madhubani art
3. Rajasthani art
4. Pattachitra art
5. Applique work
6. Chhau dance
7. Terracotta art
8. Dokra art

Please keep in mind that the cost of each art form can vary depending on factors such as the size and intricacy of the piece, the reputation of the artist, and the materials used. Additionally, the cost of any given piece of art is subjective and ultimately depends on the individual buyer's perception of its value.
